---
const title = "Professional Services | Astro Akash SH";
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --gold: #d4af37; --dark: #0b0d17; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #fff; margin: 0; 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.9), rgba(0,0,0,0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506318137071-a8e063b4bc04?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');
            background-size: cover; background-attachment: fixed; line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        nav { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        nav a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        
        h1 { color: var(--gold); text-align: center; font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        
        .service-card { 
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); 
            padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); 
            margin-bottom: 25px; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .service-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .service-card i { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        h2 { margin-top: 0; color: #fff; }
        
        .cta-box { text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; padding: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
        .btn-wa { background: #25D366; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav><a href="/"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Home</a></nav>
        
        <h1>Expert Services</h1>

        <div class="service-card">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            <h2>Career & Business Timing</h2>
            <p>Stop planting seeds in winter. I analyze your Dashas to find the exact window for your next big move, job change, or business launch.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
            <h2>Relationship Alignment</h2>
            <p>Vedic compatibility (Gun Milan) updated for the modern world. Understand the unseen patterns in your connections.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
            <h2>Student Strategy</h2>
            <p>Specialized guidance for academic success and competitive exams. Align your effort with your cosmic map.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
            <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
            <h2>Practical Remedies</h2>
            <p>No complex rituals. I provide high-impact, practical remedies that fit into a modern, fast-paced lifestyle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-box">
            <p>All consultations are strictly confidential.</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/918580672809" class="btn-wa"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Book Your Session</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
